body:
Tensorboard is moving to [tensorflow/tensorboard](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorboard). 

This change may or make not make it there (@dandelion has been focusing on making this happen, which should make future contributions to Tensorboard much easier).

Can you reopen the PR over there?
